                            <comment id="16068084" author="yuanjiali" created="Thu, 29 Jun 2017 09:46:53 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt; the ReplicaMoveThread grabs lock on the Replica instance during moving, how to guarantee that the messages are not lost?&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="16069085" author="lindong" created="Thu, 29 Jun 2017 22:13:37 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/ViewProfile.jspa?name=yuanjiali&quot; class=&quot;user-hover&quot; rel=&quot;yuanjiali&quot;&gt;yuanjiali&lt;/a&gt; ReplicaMoveThread will not grab lock for the entire period of movement. The data movement involves repeated FetchRequest and ProduceRequest until the new log catches up with the exiting log. Why would message be lost?&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
